---
title: Sticky Apricot Chicken & Veggie Israeli Couscous with Yoghurt & Mint
description: Vibrant veggies and Moroccan spices combine to create this rich and colourful bowl. From the sweet, roasted veggies stirred through the couscous, to the succulent apricot-glazed chicken and cooling yoghurt, there’s so much to love in this meal tonight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-sticky-chicken-roast-veggie-israeli-couscous-684d6093.jpg
